14
00:01:01.253 --> 00:01:04.361
Alternatively, cloud-hosted
SIEM tools are maintained and

15
00:01:04.361 --> 00:01:09.605
managed by the SIEM providers, making
them accessible through the internet.

16
00:01:09.605 --> 00:01:14.331
Cloud-hosted SIEM tools are ideal for
organizations that don't want to

17
00:01:14.331 --> 00:01:18.459
invest in creating and
maintaining their own infrastructure.

18
00:01:19.459 --> 00:01:24.410
